These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, spy, time-travel, disaster
City: miami, hamburg, nizza, berlin
1. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
2. the person traveling to berlin is on the far left##1
3. the person traveling to nizza is between the person traveling to hamburg and the person watching spy movies##2
4. the person watching disaster movies is on the far left##1
5. the person watching time-travel movies is between the person watching spy movies and the person watching comedy movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster         | spy   | time-travel | comedy       |
| City      | berlin | miami | nizza   | hamburg |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, punk, reggae, metal
There are 4 different favourite colors: lavender, purple, white, grey
1. the person who likes grey is between the fan reggae and the person who likes purple##2
2. the fan metal is on the far right##1
3. the person who likes white is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
4. the fan electronic is on the left of the person who likes lavender##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Music-Genre         | punk | electronic | reggae | metal |
| Color   | purple    | grey   | lavender | white       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, singing, filmmaking, video-games
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rugby, water-polo, soccer, biathlon
1. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
2. the person who's sport is soccer is between the person who's sport is water-polo and the person who's hobby is singing##2
3. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
5. the person who's hobby is singing is the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Hobby          | video-games    | collecting | singing   | filmmaking  |
| Sport   | water-polo | soccer   | biathlon | rugby |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-4::.
City: san-francisco, miami, marseilles, boston
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, disaster, epic, spy
1. the person watching disaster movies is the person traveling to miami##1
2. the person traveling to san-francisco is between the person watching documentary movies and the person traveling to boston##2
3. the person watching disaster movies is on the far right##1
4. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |   2    |     3      |    4     |
| City     | boston   | san-francisco    | marseilles       | miami   |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | spy | documentary | disaster |

