.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-5::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: lavender, fuchsia, ebony, turquise
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, surfing, badminton, tennis
1. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1
2. the person who's sport is badminton is on the far left##1
3. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far right##1
4. the person who likes turquise is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person who's sport is surfing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |    2     |     3     |       4       |
| Color   | lavender        | ebony | turquise  | fuchsia |
| Sport      | badminton | surfing  | tennis | cricket    |

