.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-6::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, zinnia, bellflower, daffodil
There 4 different types of food: carrot, nectarine, pumpkin, banana
1. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1
2. the person who growsdaffodil is the person eating pumpkin##1
3. the person who growsdaffodil is on the far right##1
4. the person who growszinnia is the person eating carrot##1
5. the person who growsbellflower is between the person who growsamaryllis and the person who growszinnia##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Flower   | zinnia     | bellflower           | amaryllis | daffodil  |
| Food         | carrot | banana | nectarine   | pumpkin |

