.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-7::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, turquise, light-blue, purple
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, june, november, august
1. the person who likes turquise is the person who's birthday is in february##1
2. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
3. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1
4. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
5. the person who likes apricot is between the person who's birthday is in february and the person who likes light-blue##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Color   | purple   | turquise | apricot | light-blue      |
| Birthday     | november | february    | june  | august |

