.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-8::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: sunflower, rose, zinnia, tulip
There 4 different types of food: potato, carrot, nectarine, peach
1. the person eating potato is the person who growsrose##1
2. the person eating carrot is between the person who growszinnia and the person eating nectarine##2
3. the person who growssunflower is on the far left##1
4. the person eating potato is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |       2       |     3      |     4      |
| Flower       | sunflower | tulip | zinnia     | rose   |
| Food   | nectarine   | carrot     | peach | potato |

