.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-9::.
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, thai, japanese, indian
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, mystery, family, spy
1. the japanese is between the person watching horror movies and the mexican##2
2. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the mexican##1
3. the indian is on the right of the mexican##1
4. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
5. the mexican is on the left of the person watching family movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |      4       |
| Nationality         | thai | japanese | mexican | indian |
| Movie-Genre   | horror         | spy       | mystery    | family         |

