.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-10::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, tiparillo, bolivar, old-henry
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, december, july, may
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the bolivar-smoker##1
3. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
5. the person who's birthday is in december is between the tiparillo-smoker and the person who's birthday is in may##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Cigar    | old-henry   | bolivar      | tiparillo   | siglo  |
| Birthday   | may | december | july | february |

