.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-12::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, bluemaster, pall-mall, swisher
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, sailing, water-polo, baseball
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is the bluemaster-smoker##1
2. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
3. the person who's sport is volleyball is the baccarat-smoker##1
4. the pall-mall-smoker is the person who's sport is sailing##1
5. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
6. the person who's sport is sailing is between the bluemaster-smoker and the swisher-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |     4      |
| Cigar         | bluemaster | pall-mall | swisher | baccarat |
| Sport   | water-polo          | sailing     | baseball  | volleyball     |

