.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-13::.
4 different games are played: scrabble, canasta, billiard, go
There 4 different types of food: lime, cranberry, apple, kiwi
1. the person eating apple is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
2. the person playing go is between the person eating kiwi and the person playing scrabble##2
3. the person eating cranberry is on the far right##1
4. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person eating apple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2        |    3     |     4     |
| Game           | scrabble | go | canasta | billiard     |
| Food   | lime   | apple    | kiwi   | cranberry |

