.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-15::.
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, malaysian, dutch, canadian
4 different games are played: backgammon, monopoly, mah-jongg, scrabble
1. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the malaysian##1
2. the canadian is between the person playing scrabble and the nigerian##2
3. the malaysian is on the right of the canadian##1
4. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the canadian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |      4       |
| Nationality         | nigerian      | canadian | malaysian  | dutch |
| Game   | monopoly | mah-jongg  | scrabble | backgammon    |

