.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-16::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, april, august, may
4 different games are played: chess, snooker, scrabble, billiard
1. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
2. the person who's birthday is in may is the person playing scrabble##1
3. the person who's birthday is in august is between the person playing scrabble and the person who's birthday is in april##2
4. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
5. the person playing chess is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |   3    |    4     |
| Birthday   | june | april | august | may |
| Game     | chess     | snooker   | billiard | scrabble  |

