2. the person drinking sprite is the person who's sport is rowing##1
3. the person who's sport is water-polo is between the person who's sport is sailing and the person drinking milk##2
4. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
5. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | sprite | milk | almond-milk | 7up |
| Sport           | rowing  | lacrosse  | water-polo | sailing      |

