2. the french is on the far left##1
3. the person who likes aquamarine is between the french and the person who likes emerald##2
4. the person who likes white is the french##1
5. the person who likes azure is on the right of the malaysian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2    |       3       |     4      |
| Color       | white | aquamarine | emerald | azure |
| Nationality   | french    | argentine  | malaysian    | mexican       |

