.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-19::.
House: art-deco, ranch-style, farmhouse, colonial
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, may, december, august
1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
3. the colonial house is the person who's birthday is in july##1
4. the person who's birthday is in august is between the art-deco house and the farmhouse house##2
5. the farmhouse house is the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| House   | colonial   | art-deco   | ranch-style | farmhouse |
| Birthday         | july | may | august     | december    |

