.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-20::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, bellflower, marigold, balloon-flower
There 4 different types of food: apricot, peach, orange, pomegranate
1. the person eating peach is on the far left##1
2. the person who growsdaffodil is between the person eating apricot and the person who growsballoon-flower##2
3. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
4. the person who growsbellflower is on the far right##1
5. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person eating orange##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Flower   | marigold    | balloon-flower     | daffodil | bellflower |
| Food     | peach | pomegranate | orange       | apricot     |

 